{"tid":2179117,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【蘋聞追Click】「港版袁木」因乜語無倫次？前新聞統籌專員同你睇真啲","createTime":"2020-08-29T01:20:19.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-29T02:54:01.000Z","uid":51271,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"7133c49fc19e1fad9434e4e3fe92e83a9d53a487","tid":2179117,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T01:20:19.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200829/4WLSR7HGLFB5PG7YBRFEHLZB5M/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200829%2F4WLSR7HGLFB5PG7YBRFEHLZB5M%2F&d=aJB%2Bq6ruafnyRbkwc%2FW5ZktjIx4W8g%2FGk507jgkcous%3D&h=6a16fe06\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200829%2F4WLSR7HGLFB5PG7YBRFEHLZB5M%2F&h=c94cf944\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200829/4WLSR7HGLFB5PG7YBRFEHLZB5M/</a><br />\n<br />\n全文入去睇，我只quote一兩句:<br />\n<br />\n何安達形容每次記者會也是警隊表現誠信時機，<strong>「7.21係全港甚至全世界焦點，你就喺呢啲問題上縱容？有些人對警隊有懷疑，甚至有敵意，多多少少係自己造成，唔怪得人。」<br />\n</strong><br />\n比較政府記者會過往表現，他指自己任職政府時會牢記大學恩師、<strong>前立法局主席黃宏發一句，「你做公職人員，你唔可以估人哋嘅動機」，亦可視作為官道德標準，但反觀現時由特首到各級官員卻似乎未能做到。</strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"xx-large\">他建議戾氣太大的警員，警隊訓練應安排靜修、反省，「識得叫後生仔反思，咁佢哋自己都應該真係停一停，諗一諗，當初為咩要做警察？」</span></strong>"},{"pid":"2710932d794b9da6cd6876f38a227853bc70acc4","tid":2179117,"uid":51271,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T01:21:33.000Z","msg":"當初為咩要做警察？<br />\n<br />\n你真係睇得太清高，薪高糧準唔撚駛做，有宿舍，有水炮車屌，食冰，私了，為所欲為，就係要做警賊既原因"},{"pid":"5e22ea177cf6f3361455df88b359df1b4087ccd2","tid":2179117,"uid":57674,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T01:23:18.000Z","msg":"為咩要做警察 為錢為權力囉<br />\n唔通為正義咩屌你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n十個有七個讀唔撚掂書死入去架啦<br />\n鬼叫做狗體能訓練咁易考到咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/fac